article:
'Beginnings' may refer to:

In 'music':
* ''Beginnings'' (Ambrose Slade album)
* ''Beginnings'' (The Allman Brothers Band album)
* ''Beginnings'' (Steve Howe album)
* ''Beginnings'' (Memento album)
* ''Beginnings'' (Happy the Man album), an album by Happy the Man
* "Beginnings" (song), a song by Chicago
* "Beginnings", a song by [[Mark Gormley]]

In 'literature':
* ''Beginnings'' (collection), a collection of short stories and poems by Gordon
  R. Dickson
* [[Beginnings: Geomancy, Builders' Rites and Electional Astrology in the
  European Tradition]], a book by Nigel Pennick
* [[Beginnings: The Story of Origins, of Mankind, Life, the Earth, the
  Universe]], a Big History book by Isaac Asimov

In 'other uses':
* "Beginnings" (''Fraggle Rock'' episode)
* "Beginnings", an episode of ''Spaced''
* "Beginnings", the two-part premiere episode of [[Power Rangers S.P.D.]].
